  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ComparableSet
    This interface extends the Set interface and implements the Comparable interface.
    Lattice
    Representation of a concept lattice.
    Relation
    Representation of a context, i.e. a binary relation between a set of objects and a set of attributes.

    This class implements the ComparableSet interface and extends java.util.HashSet.
